This cycle, more local candidates ran for races up and down the ballot than ever before (to my recollection).

And that’s a great thing.

(1/2)

Here in Arkansas, a lot of races could come down to a handful of votes.

So here’s what you can do:

🗳  Vote early

🚪  Knock doors for a candidate
🚘  Give a friend a ride to the polls

Let’s go.

Just a hunch.
